headline: FDA Approves Label Update for Kite’s Yescarta® for Relapsed/Refractory Primary Central Nervous System Lymphoma
summary: SANTA MONICA, Calif., February 06, 2026--Kite, a Gilead Company (Nasdaq: GILD), today announced the U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) approved an update to the Yescarta® (axicabtagene ciloleucel) prescribing information removing the previous Limitations of Use in patients with relapsed or refractory (R/R) primary central nervous system lymphoma (PCNSL). The updated label reinforces the robust safety data of Yescarta in eligible patients with R/R PCNSL; Yescarta is the only CAR T-cell thera
